function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(convPostFight, idActor)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(convPostFight)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorLorath, 0.25)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(actorLorath, egChannel)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(actorLorath, egRope)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(actorLorath)
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(actorLorath, "AnimKey_Neutral")
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(actorDonan, 0.4)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(actorDonan, egChannel)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(actorDonan, egRope)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(actorDonan)
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(actorDonan, "AnimKey_Neutral")
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(actorDonan)
	
	Hydra.ActorDelete(actorBubble)
end

--set up donan
